{"tid":1334354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［721］散步注意事直","createTime":"2019-07-20T05:29:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T06:04:13.000Z","uid":23830,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"88e5db4fe500dac89015eb95c5ddbe39a2dcbf8d","tid":1334354,"uid":23830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T05:29:07.000Z","msg":"除咗和理非最好有gear之外，大家都要留意下，721條路咁短有啲似沙田，故要留意克警會不會在告士打道一帶調動，從銅鑼灣向灣仔推進步署形成前後夾攻，多數在入黑後行動，而必一字排陣在大佛口附近阻止任何示威者進金鐘，所以若有人乘地鐵往中環或上環返轉頭行向金鐘灣仔就幾好玩了。<br />\n<br />\n另銅鑼灣真係要人多時佔SOGO一帶同克警拉鋸下，扯散其兵力。至於藍絲同黑社會必聚在終點引發事端，因為要交差才有水派，所以要小心。<br />\n<br />\n明天在銅鑼灣要玩幾轉及做下哨兵周圍看有咩地方有狗聚集。<br />\n<br />\n加油💪🏻。<br />\n<br />\nBe water。"},{"pid":"a6bf5082342de5cf38f9d02559da0e257edc62b4","tid":1334354,"uid":263221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T05:30:13.000Z","msg":"721<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbb9ed82d35466077d32b3c6ad342ed5df4b8f20","tid":1334354,"uid":259043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T05:32:58.000Z","msg":"721post上熱門"},{"pid":"27e594db9c3a9332864fa9a81a383bc4d2c9921e","tid":1334354,"uid":89882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T05:33:54.000Z","msg":"推 聽日見"},{"pid":"7eb043419d32f270f2995a18343ea36e4a7a69c3","tid":1334354,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T05:34:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[沙盤推演] 大家有無諗過呢場抗爭既end game係點?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1334346\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1334346</a>"},{"pid":"9c06f893e13875679b8dfbe07cd0764c091de0db","tid":1334354,"uid":4926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T05:35:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e